item.title: CVE-2022-36885|2024-08-03T10:14:29.453Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20github%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins GitHub Plugin 1.34.4 and earlier uses a non-constant time comparison function when checking whether the provided and computed webhook signatures are equal, allowing attackers to use statistical methods to obtain a valid webhook signature.
